{"tid":1555933,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩元朗連儂牆有藍屍狗男女撕野","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:42:45.000Z","uid":10214,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a90d5f9df373185c278d8d8a8b277347972caf9","tid":1555933,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"雖然話撕一貼百<br />\n但始終會有人睇唔過眼<br />\n隻狗乸一路撕<br />\n啲人一路圍住佢嚟影<br />\n雙方爭執僵持左一陣<br />\n直到有個巴打過嚟嗌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n我地和應<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n對狗男女先敗走<br />\n面對班無明辯是非能力嘅蠻人<br />\n用聲音擊退佢地都係一個好方法<br />\n暴動罪坐十碌呢個代價對我嚟講太沉重<br />\n原諒我始終有野割捨唔到<br />\n但其實每個人都發句聲<br />\n個威力可以好大"},{"pid":"5868a1835b1a03d811d4eb5d013c3e441e528a75","tid":1555933,"uid":278568,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"人都唔敢打 仲話時代<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命</span><br />\n用聲音喎我不如用condom<br />\n等第日佢拎刀咪繼續叫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fb8f00425ca367f231ea0d03b7606277b277c0","tid":1555933,"uid":10214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5868a1835b1a03d811d4eb5d013c3e441e528a75","tid":1555933,"uid":278568,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"人都唔敢打 仲話時代<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命</span><br />\n用聲音喎我不如用condom<br />\n等第日佢拎刀咪繼續叫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"有發聲總好過唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢拎得刀嘅我唔洗你教都知要點做<br />\n每個人都有決定自己點做嘅權利<br />\n唔係個個人都有覺悟企到前線<br />\n言論咁尖酸刻薄<br />\n你只會影衰緊勇武"},{"pid":"df654b310ab2aae269430a80e794b4adbff746fc","tid":1555933,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T19:40:40.000Z","msg":"打啦"},{"pid":"78b9be3365a21585c7e4b5b5256ff845d